Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是由…什麼組成的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是討論的血肉之軀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外在形狀雖然也是一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被稱為「內面」的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.17,0:00:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換個說法也行 就是性質
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造就「那個」的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由與生俱來的資質決定的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.57,0:00:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是取決於後天的成長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是由「那個」而生的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.02,0:00:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點變成「那個」的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還差一點就能抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道光…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道光似乎要傳達些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 小夜很壯實的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你很壯實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊 女孩子一而再再而三地摔傷臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一而再再而三啦 臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔倒 撞倒 衝撞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是傷到臉也要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 這點也能說明你是在專心打坐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做早課麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 光又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:03:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你抓住了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我伸出手 它卻還在逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近你經常看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 雖然似曾相識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 還是記不起是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是巫女的你的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾在夢與現實的縫隙中悟到了神諭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見到的那道光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許預示著某個未來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是為了助我完成「狩獵」的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要是想到什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就立刻告訴父親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有啊 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是早上在隔壁吃早飯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不換衣服 時間就不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}大空之風
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你又擦傷鼻尖了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然很莽撞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只是有點急性子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的 總是在給父親添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到添麻煩 唯芳先生也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一樣頑固不化 不知變通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啦 父親又直爽又溫柔 還很強壯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜真的是很喜歡父親呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是能多幫父親一點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我做什麼事情都還不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那種事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜你一直在努力 非常努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 出門的時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 還有10分鐘啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別急 慢慢喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣好晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空無垠 蔚藍無際
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土司雞蛋 美味咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:07:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒來由的 心情棒極
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣好晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準時起床 完成工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶飛飛 螞蟻忙碌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒極棒極 好心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣好晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒來由的 輕飄飄 輕飄飄…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天趕上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 總算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天沒有迷路的孩子麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天沒有遇上困難的老婆婆麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 只是路上有些亂扔的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會都清理掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜沒能拿到垃圾車那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我都清理好丟到垃圾堆裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都會在路上捲入各種麻煩 然後遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老好人要到什麼程度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天沒遲到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒只說今天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一周怎麼都會遲到兩次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我道歉有什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優花好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像望子成龍的媽媽一樣可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉打斷你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可老師就要來咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 這麼吵吵嚷嚷的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啦 我覺得很有趣 想看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的小品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是小品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說笑的時候吐槽果然還是很重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:08:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰吐槽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nice吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 雖然你們聊得開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要上課了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小品午休再繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香奈子老師也這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐槽是很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充愣也很重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時真同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到得堂而皇之啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒誠意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 就按慣例來點名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 這槽點太難吐槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一如既往的帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你的運動神經真的很好欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都這樣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 沒怎麼變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 運動會的時候很牛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和家人一起全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 爸爸有神職 很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼值得道歉的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的確是我小學時去世的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是文人先生就一直給我做便當 來給我加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你鄰居咖啡店的老闆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 因為我和父親都不會做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:11:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就會做好多 帶來給我們吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親和那個文人先生 都是好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 一起回家怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現有家店蛋糕很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 可明天有祭祀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得早點回去幫父親的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼 好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得很可惜呢 好吃的蛋糕沒得吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因為這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 你回家小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 鞆總班長也小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不趕緊回去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「狩獵」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來正殿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「古物」即將出現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八卦顯示的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在祭祀前占卜的吉祥八卦中出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥吧 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生魂 足魂 玉留魂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天常立尊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國常立尊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「古物」消滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 幹得好 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把御神刀擦拭一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握得太緊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.91,0:21:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 洗澡水開了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換一下衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.28,0:23:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜今天上課也趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.49,0:23:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說並不是每天都遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.34,0:23:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是遇到有麻煩的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.80,0:23:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是找到小狗 就…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來那隻小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.35,0:23:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會喜歡上我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一天一定要抱一抱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那個時候為止小夜不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.78,0:24:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話 Blood-C
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.74,0:24:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你
